strike, cutting 7,480 megawatts of electricity from nuclear
stations at 8 a.m. Paris time,  Reuters reported , citing an
unidentified union official.  The power reductions occurred at nine plants, according to
Reuters. Unions in the nationâ€™s power and gas companies have
